title: Data counter and speed meter
description:
Data counter helps monitor data usage according your plan to avoid extra costs and save your money on phone bill.  


FEATURES
# Monitor mobile data for home network
# Monitor mobile data for roaming network
# Monitor data usage by installed application (roaming, mobile, Wi-Fi)
# Several time plans (daily, weekly, monthly, custom period)
# Warning for reaching limit at 75%, 85%, 90%, 95%, 100%
# Notification shows used limit, current internet speed, used mobile/roaming data, used Wi-Fi data
# Highly customizable widget shows used limit, current internet speed, used mobile/roaming data, used Wi-Fi data
# Option to add extra data package
